Quellious Server Nagafen Raid<P>Ok now before you read this, know this.  It is now 11:39 PM where I am.  I started on this raid at 5PM.  It was a naggy raid.  We had a nice group on the way in.  We got lots of XP on FGs cause we were a good group.  I was having lots of fun.<P>Now here it comes.  It may be because I'm cranky cause I've got work tommorow.  But here it is:<P>We killed Naggy with 4 loses ( I didn't die! w00t! ) which is pretty good.  Someone went to loot (Blylighter or something).  He got a "You cannot loot this corpse, someone else is already looting it" message.  He clicked again and it went through.  However, something was wrong.  He didn't get any money.  Has anyone EVER seen nagafen not drop so much as a copper?  Me neither.  The dragon had 3 items on him.  The gold plated thingy, the book for pallies and the drums for bards.  Now WAIT a minute.  Where's... ANYTHING?  We came to the conclusion that someone had ninja looted the corpse.  Well, we are pretty pissed off.  The raid leader ONLY gives a tell to a guide to get a GM.  They have to wait.  FINE.  We wait an hour, finally they talk to a GM (Catalyst whom you'll see later).  The GM tells them there is nothing they can do.  Now I personally KNOW this is wrong.  They have logs of EVERYTHING, they could go check.  So the raid leader and the GM argue for about another hour and nothing turns out.  Well, I (being the optimistic one and hoping no one really ninja looted) gave a tell to this GM and here is what ensued:<P><I><BR>[Tue May 08 23:17:41 2001] Players in EverQuest:<BR>[Tue May 08 23:17:41 2001] ---------------------------<BR>[Tue May 08 23:17:41 2001] * GM-Admin *[60 Sorcerer] Zelorixa (Dark Elf) <Order of Quellious> ZONE: wakening<BR>[Tue May 08 23:17:41 2001] * Guide *[50 Ranger] Catalyst (Wood Elf) <Order of Quellious> ZONE: warslikswood<BR>[Tue May 08 23:17:41 2001] [ANONYMOUS] <BR>[Tue May 08 23:17:41 2001] There are 3 players in EverQuest.<BR>[Tue May 08 23:17:44 2001] Zainenn begins to cast a spell.<BR>[Tue May 08 23:17:44 2001] Tenuvas shouts, 'Lol Someone Ninja Loot?'<BR>[Tue May 08 23:17:44 2001] Thorvin shouts, 'ok....i hate untrusting people'<BR>[Tue May 08 23:17:46 2001] Calell says, 'Heal Please someone '<BR><B>[Tue May 08 23:17:52 2001] You told Catalyst, 'Does Naggy always drop money?'</B><BR>[Tue May 08 23:17:59 2001] Xria begins to cast a spell.<BR>[Tue May 08 23:18:01 2001] Abednego shouts, 'god that is unbelievable...wee my first bad gm experience *a tear*'<BR>[Tue May 08 23:18:01 2001] Pyrrolin shouts, 'we don't know if ninjaed for sure'<BR>[Tue May 08 23:18:04 2001] Calell feels much better.<BR>[Tue May 08 23:18:04 2001] Fandryl shouts, 'someone got away with something'<BR>[Tue May 08 23:18:10 2001] Abednego shouts, 'but there was no money pyrrolin'<BR>[Tue May 08 23:18:16 2001] You cannot remove this effect.<BR>[Tue May 08 23:18:17 2001] You cannot remove this effect.<BR>[Tue May 08 23:18:23 2001] Shirl shouts, 'what a screwjob'<BR>[Tue May 08 23:18:23 2001] Grongl shouts, 'Ok - the lesson for the day is - Have the leader of the xp group verify loot!'<BR>[Tue May 08 23:18:28 2001] Najort shouts, 'well congrats to the guy who got away with stealing i hope u get herpes!!'<BR>[Tue May 08 23:18:32 2001] Your heroism fades.<BR>[Tue May 08 23:18:37 2001] Pyrrolin shouts, 'many people like to look and see what is there but don't take anything, can't be positive'<BR>[Tue May 08 23:18:40 2001] Abednego shouts, 'he's long camped by now'<BR>[Tue May 08 23:18:42 2001] Players in EverQuest:<BR>[Tue May 08 23:18:42 2001] ---------------------------<BR>[Tue May 08 23:18:42 2001] [ANONYMOUS] <BR>[Tue May 08 23:18:42 2001] * GM-Admin *[60 Sorcerer] Zelorixa (Dark Elf) <Order of Quellious> ZONE: wakening<BR>[Tue May 08 23:18:42 2001] * Guide *[50 Ranger] Catalyst (Wood Elf) <Order of Quellious> ZONE: warslikswood<BR>[Tue May 08 23:18:42 2001] [ANONYMOUS] <BR>[Tue May 08 23:18:42 2001] There are 4 players in EverQuest.<BR>[Tue May 08 23:18:44 2001] Players in EverQuest:<BR>[Tue May 08 23:18:44 2001] ---------------------------<BR>[Tue May 08 23:18:44 2001] [ANONYMOUS] <BR>[Tue May 08 23:18:44 2001] [ANONYMOUS] <BR>[Tue May 08 23:18:44 2001] * GM-Admin *[60 Sorcerer] Zelorixa (Dark Elf) <Order of Quellious> ZONE: wakening<BR>[Tue May 08 23:18:44 2001] * Guide *[50 Ranger] Catalyst (Wood Elf) <Order of Quellious> ZONE: warslikswood<BR>[Tue May 08 23:18:44 2001] [ANONYMOUS] <BR>[Tue May 08 23:18:44 2001] There are 5 players in EverQuest.<BR><B>[Tue May 08 23:18:48 2001] Catalyst tells you, 'Petition Please'</B><BR>[Tue May 08 23:18:48 2001] Pyrrolin shouts, 'all we can do is keep an eye on our suspects'<BR>[Tue May 08 23:18:54 2001] Raloren shouts, 'not to be devils advocate, but why you guys wait so lon to loot?'<BR>[Tue May 08 23:18:56 2001] Abednego shouts, 'who are suspects then'<BR>[Tue May 08 23:18:57 2001] Macheenhead says out of character, 'what about the person who trained us earlier?'<BR>[Tue May 08 23:18:59 2001] Gadal says out of character, 'who are they?'<BR>[Tue May 08 23:19:07 2001] Fandryl shouts, 'did they even check our suspects?'<BR><B>[Tue May 08 23:19:10 2001] You told Catalyst, 'A simple yes or no question and you answer petition please?'</B><BR>[Tue May 08 23:19:11 2001] Thorvin shouts, 'this loot.....WE NEED THIS LOOT : )'<BR>[Tue May 08 23:19:14 2001] Najort shouts, 'im outa here i cant believe i wated so long'<BR>[Tue May 08 23:19:16 2001] Frere shouts, 'you can shut up too'<BR><B>[Tue May 08 23:19:17 2001] Catalyst tells you, 'Yes, petition'</B><BR>[Tue May 08 23:19:20 2001] Taking a screenshot...<BR>[Tue May 08 23:19:22 2001] Pyrrolin shouts, 'advice for future raids, have leader of exp group loot immediately'<BR>[Tue May 08 23:19:23 2001] Zelorixa BROADCASTS, 'All zones are back up! Thank you for your patience tonight! If you died in Skyshrine, Wakening Lands, Plane of Mischief, Eastern Wastes or Crystal Caverns as a result of the crash, please petition for resurrection.'<BR><B>[Tue May 08 23:19:29 2001] You told Catalyst, 'does naggy drop money every time?'</B><BR>[Tue May 08 23:19:33 2001] Raloren shouts, 'i dont mean to be rude just asking =('<BR>[Tue May 08 23:19:42 2001] Taking a screenshot...<BR><B>[Tue May 08 23:19:45 2001] Catalyst tells you, 'Ask me again after you have been told to petition, and I will give you a warning'</B><BR>[Tue May 08 23:19:50 2001] Fandryl shouts, 'are the GM's even prepared to check the logs of our suspects?'<BR>[Tue May 08 23:19:56 2001] Thorvin shouts, 'i'm outta here'<BR>[Tue May 08 23:20:03 2001] Najort shouts, 'HOW ARE WE SOPOSED TO RESPECT GMS WHEN IN REALITY THEY CANT DO NOTHING FOR U BUT THEY CAN DO STUFF AGAINST u'<BR>[Tue May 08 23:20:08 2001] Macheenhead says out of character, 'GM's are lame :P'<BR><B>[Tue May 08 23:20:13 2001] You told Catalyst, 'ok, I'll stop, but you bet this is going up on Castersrealm tommorow'</B><BR>[Tue May 08 23:20:18 2001] Calell begins to cast a spell.<BR>[Tue May 08 23:20:18 2001] Grongl says out of character, 'GMs eat it'<BR>[Tue May 08 23:20:19 2001] Zainenn begins to cast a spell.<BR>[Tue May 08 23:20:22 2001] Najort shouts, 'LOL everyone already left'<BR>[Tue May 08 23:20:24 2001] Senini begins to cast a spell.<BR>[Tue May 08 23:20:24 2001] Taking a screenshot...<BR><B>[Tue May 08 23:20:25 2001] Catalyst tells you, 'OK then. Have fun'</B><BR>[Tue May 08 23:20:28 2001] Calell begins to cast a spell.<BR><B>[Tue May 08 23:20:31 2001] You told Catalyst, 'I will    <IMG SRC="smile.gif" border="0">'</I></B><P>Sound a little rude to you?  Yeah, me too.  Well, if you think I made this log up (yeah yeah, logs can be messed with) I ALSO took screenshots of this whole 2 minute conversation.  Screenshots are a tad harder to mess with.  Anyway, this is utter bull****.  I've given tells to MANY GM's before and had a yes or no answer given and even long lengthy ones explained to me.  Hell, I mean "Petition please" takes longer to write than YES OR NO.  Could it have been that difficult?  ARGH!  I don't even want the loot.  I don't want anything except to know who this ninja looter is, and to kick the living SH*T out of this GM right now. <BR> <BR>Before I head off to bed, I should tell you I happen to know a Senior Guide personally.  They do have logs they can check.  They can do a lot of cool stuff.  Most GM/guides are cool.  But there's always the bad apples. *sigh*  Warn my account will you..grrrr...<P>Man, I need some sleep...<P>--------------------<P><I>I'll keep ticking until the caffeine stops kicking. - Poak Debak <P>Cazic Thule shouts,"CORPHEOUS!"<BR>Corpheous shouts,"What?"<BR>Cazic Thule shouts,"CORPHEOUS!"<BR>Corpheous shouts,"WHAT?"<BR>Cazic Thule shouts,"CORPHEOUS DAMMIT!"<BR>Corpheous shouts,"WHAT DO YOU WANT?"<BR>Cazic Thule shouts,"NOOO! I've been nerfed!"<P>The world is a playground, obey the rules and have fun.  Disobey the rules, and you won't be able to play anymore.<P>Do not meddle in the affairs of dragons, for you are crunchy, and taste good with ketchup.</I>
